{"tid":1517802,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[討論] 預先司法復核林鄭用緊急法既權力","createTime":"2019-08-30T04:40:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T04:40:14.000Z","uid":314892,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8947d9a2e790a215854b9a0cebd910a92291cd8b","tid":1517802,"uid":314892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T04:40:14.000Z","msg":"唔洗講大家都知緊急法既權力係大到痴綫<br />\n根據蘋果日報呢單分析 <a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190830/59989188\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190830%2F59989188&d=Fe1Xron1KfJbBj576sEg8v3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=13feb7fb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190830%2F59989188&h=dcec1bec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190830/59989188</a> 緊急法係違憲既 （留意緊急法係基本法同香港人權法案條例之前通過的）<br />\n既然係甘 係咪可以預先司法復核 要求法庭判決緊急法究竟係咪違憲 （或者有咩林鄭係唔做得？）<br />\n法庭有可能會聼 （利申本人並非法律界） 因爲緊急法一頒佈左就有效 頒佈後再復核就難 （警察係法庭門口拉鳩你都得） 仲可能有好多人係緊急法頒佈後被捕坐監 但係頒佈緊急法前復核起碼安全D <br />\n唔知大家覺得值唔值得?"}]}